Package: WaterDetection
Title: Water Detection for Dam level control (or lakes, bodies of water etc) using pre-processed Sentinel-2 imagery
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Pedro", "Fernandes", , "pedro.pires.fernandes@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Takes composite Sentinel-2 imagery (with 10 bands) and runs an algorythm that detects water based on a combination of RGB and NDVI values. Exports pixel data as .CSV and builds time series graphs
